ers create  million liberia fund washington business journal retrieved september     a b smith ben  bob johnson on obamas past  ben smith politicocom retrieved    drugs race raised in clintonobama fight cnn  january   drugs race raised in clintonobama fight cnn  january   the hypocrisy of bets bob johnsons obama smears  rlj development llc january    johnson cites race in obamas surge  sheila johnson marrying very well washingtonpostcom  retrieved  may    heil emily roberts roxanne  bet founder bob johnson engaged to lauren wooden the washington post issn  retrieved    a b heil emily  may  bet founder bob johnson weds lauren wooden at napa valley ceremony washingtonpostcom the washington post retrieved  may   external linksedit official website johnson sets sights on new urban cable network robert l johnson interview video at the archive of american television appearances on cspan authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlerobertljohnsonoldid categories  birthsafricanamerican billionairesafricanamerican company foundersafricanamerican sports executives and administratorsamerican billionairesamerican mass media ownersamerican television executivesbusinesspeople from charlotte north carolinabusinesspeople from illinoisbusinesspeople from mississippicharlotte bobcats ownerscharlotte sting ownersliving peoplepeople from freeport illinoispeople from hickory mississippipeople from kosciusko mississippiuniversity of illinois at urbana–champaign alumniwomens national basketball association executiveswoodrow wilson school of public and international affairs alumnihidden categories pages with reference errorspages with duplicate reference namesarticles with hcardsno local image but image on wikidataarticles using templateemmytvlegends namewikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with lccn identifiers navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article tal